OL,3,CCouncil agrees to make City Ground
OL,4,Cland available for sale to Nottingham
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,FNottingham City Council has formally
OL,8,Fagreed to make the City Ground land
OL,9,Favailable for sale to Nottingham
OL,10,FForest.
OL,12,FThe football club have been playing at
OL,13,Fthe City Ground stadium since 1898,
OL,14,Fbut it had reached a stalemate on
OL,15,Fwhether the council would renew the
OL,16,Fclub's lease.
OL,18,FExecutive members of the council met
OL,19,Fon Tuesday, July 16, and agreed to put
OL,20,Fthe freehold up for sale to the club.
