OL,7,F"So now that means we have done
OL,8,Feverything within Nottingham City
OL,9,FCouncil to get the approval to get
OL,10,Fthat deal done. Now all will be
OL,11,Fsubject to signing legal contracts."
OL,13,FCouncil documents state it is looking
OL,14,Fto finish the sale and receive the
OL,15,Fmoney in the 2024/25 financial year,
OL,16,Fwhich ends in March next year.
OL,18,FIn a statement, the club said last
OL,19,Fweek that the purchase is reliant on
OL,20,Fthe ability to expand the stadium and
OL,21,Fmake big changes.
