OL,7,FIt said the purchase is "entirely
OL,8,Fconditional on Nottingham Forest first
OL,9,Fbeing granted the relevant permissions
OL,10,Fthat will allow us to realise our
OL,11,Fhugely ambitious plans our hugely
OL,12,Fambitious plans for a significantly
OL,13,Flarger stadium capacity, world-class
OL,14,Fhospitality spaces and associated
OL,15,Fsubstantial real estate development in
OL,16,Fthe vicinity of the ground."
OL,18,FNottingham Forest currently leases the
OL,19,Fland from the council, but there had
OL,20,Fbeen just 33 years left on the
OL,21,Fexisting agreement.
