OL,8,Fseen as critical so the club could
OL,9,Frealise its plans to expand the
OL,10,Fstadium.
OL,12,FBut the council asked for a larger sum
OL,13,Ffor the lease earlier this year, and
OL,14,Fnegotiations reached a stalemate.
OL,16,FThere were reports that the council
OL,17,Fwanted a rise from #250,000 a year to
OL,18,Faround #1m, following the club's
OL,19,Fpromotion to the Premier League.
