OL,7,FThe council said declared effective
OL,8,Fbankruptcy in November last year, and
OL,9,Fsaid decisions would be made on
OL,10,Ffinancial viability.
OL,12,FGovernment commissioners were also
OL,13,Fappointed in February, and they too
OL,14,Fwill be ensuring best value is
OL,15,Fachieved in all areas of council
OL,16,Foperations.
OL,18,FCllr Khan took over as leader of the
OL,19,FLabour-run authority in May, and talks
OL,20,Fresumed.
